b'Afraid To Be Cool / Raise Me Up': b'Music videos for Miyavi\'s four-track album Afraid To Be Cool / Raise Me Up. A thirty-second animated teaser for the album was released in April, featuring a sample of Raise Me Up. In May, a music video for the short version of Afraid To Be Cool was released with a similar style, but featuring original animation. The non-remixed songs were later included on his "Fire Bird" album.'
